www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/billie-eilish-lollapalooza-2023-getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/billie-eilish-lollapalooza-2023-getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/billie-eilish-lollapalooza-2023-getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/billie-eilish-lollapalooza-2023-getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">比莉·艾利什 (Billie Eilish)</a>在打破女性独唱艺术家纪录的一周内，获得了她的第二首英国冠军单曲。</p><p>这位歌手的新单曲“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-barbie-what-was-i-made-for-3468293">What Was I Made For？”</a> 《<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/films/barbie">芭比娃娃</a></em>》原声带中的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilishs-james-bond-theme-no-time-to-die-is-here-2609171">《No Time To Die》</a>成为她继 2020 年<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/james-bond">詹姆斯·邦德</a>单曲《No Time To Die》之后第二首登上英国排行榜榜首的歌曲。</p><p>该专辑还创下了女性艺人排行榜单周冠军的纪录，单曲榜前六名的位置有史以来第一次全部由女性独唱艺人占据。</p><p>本周排名第二的是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dua-lipa">杜阿·利帕 (Dua Lipa)</a>的另一首<em>芭比</em>歌曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dua-lipa-shares-lead-single-from-barbie-movie-dance-the-night-3448502">“Dance The Night”</a> ，奥利维亚·<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/olivia-rodrigo">罗德里戈 (Olivia Rodrigo)</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/olivia-rodirgo-shares-rock-opera-inspired-new-track-vampire-3463529">“Vampire”</a>排名第三，凭借<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/olivia-rodrigo-new-single-bad-idea-right-listen-official-video-watch-3481559">“Bad Idea Right?”</a>排名第六。<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift)</a>凭借<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swifts-cruel-summer-re-enters-uk-charts-four-years-after-release-3463815">复兴的《残酷夏天》(Cruel Summer)</a>排名第四，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/peggy-gou">佩吉·古 (Peggy Gou)</a>凭借《(It Goes Like) Nanana》排名第五。</p><p>进入前八名的还有由女性艺术家领衔的歌曲，其中<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nicki-minaj">Nicki Minaj</a>的《Barbie World》、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ice-spice">Ice Spice</a>和 Aqua 排名第七， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/becky-hill">Becky Hill</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chase-and-status">Chase &amp; Status</a>的《Disconnect》排名第八。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">本周的官方单曲榜打破了纪录！ <a href="https://t.co/zuNbMrJIs8">https://t.co/zuNbMrJIs8</a></p><p> — 官方图表 (@officialcharts) <a href="https://twitter.com/officialcharts/status/1692612580802519237?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 8 月 18 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>在其他地方， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-says-the-creative-process-is-different-with-her-next-album-3485296">艾利什最近公开了她在制作第三张专辑时创作过程中发生的变化</a>。</p><p>这位歌手在 Dua Lipa 的<em><a href="https://open.spotify.com/episode/1Mc30pmvv8Qaw3d50xjd5f?si=sGcbH_2PRR27gTUVXFiw4Q" target="_blank" rel="noopener">At Your Service</a></em>播客的新一集中发表讲话，解释了 18 岁到 21 岁之间的“大跃进”，以及她如何说服自己没有“失去它”。</p><p>艾利什的首张专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/billie-eilish-album-review-when-we-all-fall-asleep-where-do-we-go-2467653#:~:text=It's%20enjoyable%20and%20familiar%2C%20but,album%20does%20on%20every%20level.">当我们都入睡时，我们去哪里？</a> 》于 2019 年发行，随后于 2021 年发行了《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/billie-eilish-happier-than-ever-review-3006594">Happier Than Ever</a> 》。她现在正在制作第三张专辑，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-has-started-work-on-a-new-album-3357021">并于 11 月确认</a>她和她的兄弟/合作者<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/finneas">Finneas</a>最近“开始制作专辑”。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-scores-second-uk-number-one-in-record-breaking-week-for-female-songwriters-3485416">比莉·艾利什 (Billie Eilish) 在破纪录的一周内夺得英国第二位女性歌曲作家排行榜第一的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
